11#ifndef LOGGING_RTC_EVENT_LOG_EVENTS_RTC_EVENT_AUDIO_SEND_STREAM_CONFIG_H_
12#define LOGGING_RTC_EVENT_LOG_EVENTS_RTC_EVENT_AUDIO_SEND_STREAM_CONFIG_H_
13
14#include <memory>
15
16#include "api/rtc_event_log/rtc_event.h"
17#include "logging/rtc_event_log/rtc_stream_config.h"
18
19namespace webrtc {
20
21class RtcEventAudioSendStreamConfig final : public RtcEvent {
22 public:
23 static constexpr Type kType = Type::AudioSendStreamConfig;
24
25 explicit RtcEventAudioSendStreamConfig(
26 std::unique_ptr<rtclog::StreamConfig> config);
27 ~RtcEventAudioSendStreamConfig() override;
28
29 Type GetType() const override { return kType; }
30 bool IsConfigEvent() const override { return true; }
31
32 std::unique_ptr<RtcEventAudioSendStreamConfig> Copy() const;
33
34 const rtclog::StreamConfig& config() const { return *config_; }
35
36 private:
37 RtcEventAudioSendStreamConfig(const RtcEventAudioSendStreamConfig& other);
38
39 const std::unique_ptr<const rtclog::StreamConfig> config_;
40};
41
42struct LoggedAudioSendConfig {
43 LoggedAudioSendConfig() = default;
44 LoggedAudioSendConfig(int64_t timestamp_us, const rtclog::StreamConfig config)
45 : timestamp_us(timestamp_us), config(config) {}
46
47 int64_t log_time_us() const { return timestamp_us; }
48 int64_t log_time_ms() const { return timestamp_us / 1000; }
49
50 int64_t timestamp_us;
51 rtclog::StreamConfig config;
52};
53} // namespace webrtc
54
55#endif // LOGGING_RTC_EVENT_LOG_EVENTS_RTC_EVENT_AUDIO_SEND_STREAM_CONFIG_H_
